comments: Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lillard (POR) and the contact that occurs is marginal.
Covington (POR) cleanly deflects the incoming pass intended for Jokic (DEN).

Anthony (POR) gets both hands on the ball while defending Jokic (DEN) in the post.  Additionally, Covington (POR) gets his hand on the ball and any contact with Jokic is incidental.  Officials correctly whistle a held ball between Anthony and Jokic.
Campazzo (DEN) briefly grasps Lillard's (POR) jersey prior to the jump ball.
Jokic (DEN) places his arm to Lillard's (POR) front at the start of the drive but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Porter Jr. (DEN) contests the play at the basket by Lillard (POR) and marginal contact occurs with his arm that does not affect his shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) moves over the screen and any marginal contact is created by Lillard (POR) during his jump shot attempt.
Anthony (POR) briefly grasps Gordon's (DEN) arm and does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball during the rebound.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Campazzo (DEN).
Gordon (DEN) moves laterally into Lillard's (POR) path on the drive and affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs before Lillard is in his shooting motion.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Rivers (DEN).
Hollis-Jefferson (POR) reaches in and the contact that occurs with Campazzo's (DEN) arm is marginal.
Covington (POR) commits a take foul on Campazzo (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) moves forward towards Lillard (POR) and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt that does not affect his SQBR.
McCollum (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Campazzo (DEN) prior to the incidental contact to his body.
Powell (POR) moves into Morris (DEN) and initiates contact to the body that affects his SQBR.
McCollum (POR) gathers the ball and makes a legal move prior to his jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Morris (DEN).
Covington (POR) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Covington (POR) makes incidental contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm after the release of his shot attempt near the rim.
